overview.en: YTC stores different data in different zones. In YTC ecological blockchain, the data stored in peer-to-peer storage is fragmented and stored on the blockchain nodes in a decentralized manner. Open data confirmed by users will also be stored on the platform blockchain. The original data of sensitive personal information will be guaranteed with high security through encryption and fragmentation.
overview.zh: YTC将不同数据分区储存，在YTC生态区块链中,存储在对等储存器中的数据碎片化并以分散式储存在区块链节点上，由用户确认开放的数据也将上链储存在平台区块链上。将通过加密、碎片化的处理方式，以较高的安全性保证敏感个人信息的原始数据。
